{"tid":1630687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【NOW事件】唔係道歉：因為警方蠻橫行為令現場拍攝環境混亂對記者受傷表示遺憾","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:36:30.000Z","uid":154486,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c38ed16126cc008c7b7df669362c2f3139b955d","tid":1630687,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"因為警察蠻橫暴力行為令現場拍攝環境混亂對記者受傷表示遺憾，並重申五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n因為運動並無大台，所以警方極易派臥底喬裝成抗爭者，傷害記者並嫁禍抗爭者。<br />\n希望記者、攝影師早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣唔係道歉，只係acknowledge並做出反應，已經好過乜都唔講！！"},{"pid":"7f9e1b4ef6fbfbdab9c665f672b0020f2fc70b49","tid":1630687,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"